    "text": [
        "Dear sir,",
        "I am an English teacher named Irfan Ali, who works in a university. I went on a holiday, and I lost my laptop. I had an insurance to cover any damage which was caused by losing. I am writing this to claim for the damage.",
        "First, I lost my laptop which I got from Rawalpindi in 2018, and it was HP with 500 hard disk and 4 GB processor. It costed 25000 rupees.",
        "Secondly, I lost it while I travelled to Germany in the last month. I took a transit flight from Karachi via Dubai. While spending time in Dubai, I lost it, where I was sleeping and I did not realise until I reached Germany.",
        "Finally, as I had insured my travel with your company, so I would like you replace it with the same model, which i had with  a new one. As It is mentioned in the travel insurance document, that you can get replacement in case of anything lost!",
        "Kindly arrange it as soon as possible I will be waiting for positive response in due course.",
        "Yours faithfully",
        "Irfan Ali"
    ],
